## SSpacesSelectorComponent

This package expose a simple `SSpacesSelectorComponent` custom element that you can define and use in your pages easily.

## Features

-   Framework agnostic. Simply webcomponent.
-   ALlows you to select paddings and margins
-   Responsive props [see more](/doc/components/responsive)
-   And more...

## Usage

First, simply import and define the component in your js/ts file:

```js
import { define } from '@coffeekraken/s-spaces-selector-component';
define();
```

Make use of it in your pages:

```html
<s-spaces-selector></s-spaces-selector>
```

